人唔願意配合 順便手起刀落就人人都冇咩所謂 畢竟唔乎合經濟效益嘅事真係冇幾多人願做"},{"pid":"3a209ba3494f9b3b86d6b7544ae8993b74309fb2","tid":876919,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac8dae60a5c83fb2385d5efa981c668d2cc94ec8","tid":876919,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"30a0ee56e3e9861a8fad36f9cd3665a9145315a9","tid":876919,"uid":155558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9f6b47add8a3b6adc9f6f25a061a73244c32d87f","tid":876919,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"攞蝦條命就人道？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"你搞清楚我講咩先啦，係盡量人道，或者比較人道。<br />\n<br />\n學你講要strictly人道就根本唔攞得佢命。<br />\n<br />\n人道都有分程度。<br />\n<br />\n外國人會一槍打入牛腦等佢死直再劏。<br />\n<br />\n中國人會綁隻活生生嘅牛喺食客張枱側邊，即片一片大腿肉出嚟，即刻落煱打邊爐。<br />\n<br />\n依家西方就係推緊要食佢唔緊要，但唔好做啲嘢令佢有不必要嘅長期痛楚。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"哦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"未撚讀過梁惠王？"},{"pid":"28a41a7d937e0495d6ef3986bea260d0353b4bd0","tid":876919,"uid":130897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"有無論文link"},{"pid":"f19c809e68e8e104d85888950681e5733b24bf0c","tid":876919,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43c2e17acff8264d8d99950c004351987bb86f3","tid":876919,"uid":21699,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔好話你(理論上)知唔知人地 其實人地都好難知道你既感覺<br />\n好多時 一個人有情緒 只睇面色 其他人都好難察覺到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野你唔講出黎 人地都未必會知咩事 <br />\n就算講出黎 表達亦有可能受干擾<br />\n相反，我地要準確理解他人的情緒亦唔容易<br />\n所謂同理心、感同身受<br />\n講得好輕易 實際